 Specifies options to prevent ads from replacing or appearing with this line item. Additionally, if set to exclude none, other ads can be shown in any slots not being used by this line item. If set to exclude display ads, video ads can be shown, but no other display ads can be shown, even in slots that aren't used by this line item.
